This folder contains main code for Megumi 

speech.py is the main file for Megumi. excute this file.

udp.py use for sending UDP Packet to Arduino (Turn the lights on!).

megumi.sps is Speech Phrase Specification file you can add more pharse there. After you done adding more pharse. Run "python MakeSpeechProject.py megumi megumi.sps"

more info about .sps file: https://bitbucket.org/matthew3/speakpython/wiki/The%20SPS%20File%20Format

Don't forget to install SpeakPython and its requires module!